{"type": "article", "id": 62036, "title": "看似坚硬的木质长凳，坐下去还挺有弹性？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-03-13T23:07:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 57249, "name": "Oittm"}, {"id": 5579, "name": "Snøhetta"}, {"id": 57250, "name": "Mathieu Delacroix"}, {"id": 57251, "name": "Jaegeun Kim"}, {"id": 57252, "name": "Ricardo Garza Marcos"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 120, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190313205012mbtuXceokQLKPg92.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} </style>  </p><h3>Bend Bench by Ricardo Garza Marcos</h3><p>这款名为 Bend 的长木凳最近在 Designweek Mexico 展出，试图利用木材的垂直切割特点，使座椅有一些弹性，出自墨西哥建筑师 Ricardo Garza Marcos 之手。</p><p>他对各种类型的木材进行了测试，并对每个切割点的深度和间距进行了测试，以提供长凳的灵活性和弹性。最终，设计师选择了名为 ahuehuete 的墨西哥柏树，因为它符合制作长凳所需的强度和灵活性，整条木材上做了 87 个间隔切口和两个搁在钢架上的凹槽。</p><p>为了将木材连接到框架上，长凳主体部分被拉伸成一个平坦的座椅，给人一种坚硬表面的观感。但如果有人坐上去，座椅就开始弯曲，有柔软的，仿佛加了气垫一般的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205106yx6EKQY2rvDi7NOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.346875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205106Bt47hipkRcevWOun.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205107lwjn9QXtM3iaNApK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205106IocFPe3SKh98puXO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205107ljwDI7Je4XMHNndF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205107gHizJvwV7KdFDm1y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205107neaoT5BuMKcwrpRY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205108U07aDvnzVMGfFBWE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205107tGsg8hREwrATIdue.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>New Name and Visual Identity for the Norwegian State Railways by Snøhetta</h3><p>挪威建筑事务所 Snøhetta 为挪威国家铁路设计了全新的品牌名称和视觉形象，旨在将客运业务的各个方面统一起来，以更好地传达公司在未来提供移动服务的愿景。</p><p>挪威国家铁路在近年经历了一系列重大变革，不再持有铁路、信号系统、车站或列车，而是致力于旅客服务。公司同时还是挪威最大巴士公司 Nettbuss 的持有者。此外，集团还在瑞典运营公共汽车和火车，并通过在挪威运营电动城市汽车来向多元化的移动服务提供商转型。</p><p>为了更好地传达公司目前的运营思路，设计团队为其旗下所有的个人运输业务引入了一个共同的新名称:Vy。这个词汇来源于法语中的 vue，其词源为 voir，表示“看”的意思。在挪威语中，它也有表示观点、视角和展望的类似含义。</p><p>这个新名称能够引发一系列与旅行有关的联想，去发现新事物、获得新的视角并拓宽视野。它使我们回想起童年时在火车里看到的飞驰而过的风景，抑或是坐在在火车和公交车上，偶尔望一眼窗外的日常体验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205214Rky2sAHqtJLd6n9m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.594792\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205214YHuAezbkUFTZOmDr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.597917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205214pPvAZty2SgVnro9Q.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.542135\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205215Vv38sL6XQb4tEzPM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639583\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205215SlcRQOVTn3kxwZGD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205215XFJxdqEetom1QVLh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903132052159qB7giFVT624C3PO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639583\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205216JXTGQVHDSRd0cYFg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.426042\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205216vQsyVgfPjTSahq1D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.480208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205216oCvOJeWQxTE1S0if.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://snohetta.com/projects/427-new-name-and-visual-identity-for-the-norwegian-state-railways\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snøhetta</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The SOLEIL by Jaegeun Kim</h3><p>韩国设计师 Jaegeun Kim 设计了一款名为 SOLEIL 的创新产品，希望能够为市面上常见的烘干机提供替代方案。</p><p>与传统的烘干机不同的是，SOLEIL 可以将外部空气带入室内，内置的加热元件能够模仿太阳的温暖，提高干燥衣物的效率。值得一提的是，其内置加热元件的温度可以通过手机 App 来控制，简捷易用。</p><p>当然，它的设计也尽可能简洁，颜色和饰面都经过精挑细选，使其能够与家中其他的家具搭配起来使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205759M71Hve2cFCErI0iO.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562376\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205326KzUstElF5jyPRDd3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.618095\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205327nAFkKI106TUDZHRc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903132053276yXVqZfSgocJi1zm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019031320532857ScFsrTaxGWwOUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903132053287Xo2hNy3vauSr5G0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205328csxqInog4UTrWvzm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205328hlIcFb890762QXBG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205329o5MR2Zg674Ahtrdl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205329W5eEkypAnLiHBUOV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019031320532951N7P2Gr6nCRxFif.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205327XP9wzpVvQ31MuZCl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/2019/03/12/bring-the-warmth-of-the-sun-inside/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Oittm Intelligent Wake Up Alarm Clock</h3><p>当你有 Oittm 智能唤醒闹钟时，每天都能准时醒来。这个时钟不仅仅是告诉时间，还提供智能唤醒。后面的锥形部分实际上是完美的夜灯，它还配有湿度和温度传感器。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903132058462ITG3qm8cCbYvlwD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205846kAYLiRUGO4m96VxW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205847wtoQFpnNs2XYB8Sr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.722857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205846YkaTEgp3luiKOHVL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/2017/11/14/bedside-clock-combined-with-a-bright-idea/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Strie Chair by Mathieu Delacroix</h3><p>这款结构精巧、简约优雅的椅子，由年轻的巴黎设计师 Mathieu Delacroix 设计，  是 Cinna Young Talent Competition No.9 的决赛作品。</p><p>Strie 椅子是从简单的线型手绘画中构思出来的。两条连接在一起的黑色线条营造出一个强壮而精致的椅子骨架。这两条曲线由钢管制成，它们形成两个独特的侧框架，焊接起来，就形成了椅子的背面。可轻松堆叠，方便收纳。</p><p>椅子的主框架被绘制成一系列金属条，赋予家具轻盈的轮廓。由于其简洁纯净的外形，Strie 室内室外皆可使用。它提供了一种极简主义风格的优雅，在轻盈和力量之间实现了比例精细的平衡。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205944j2cgMfabr9PGIRUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205944ZpvUltQ54k7yg89o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205944EuQs0WPDL3CJmpfG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666449\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205944DE806efA2Uj3HsI4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498776\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205944Pvdp69isCmOhHxYD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313205944EsHpjWRZ6Gq4cFYJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.mathieudelacroix.com/#/srcs-1/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mathieu Delacroix</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}